          "summary_text": {
            "en": "Brand Name\n:         Parete\nProduct No.:\nPRT-FS662,\nPRT-FS800,\nPRT-FS1000\nMOQ:\n10 m\n2\nUnit Price:\n25 USD/m\n2\nto 80 USD/m\n2\n(Decided by technica requirements)\nPacking:\nAbout 500 m\n2\nfor 20 GP Container\nPacking Style:\nParete Logo, Neutral,  OEM logo\nProduction time:\n7 days to 30 days, 500m2, 10 days for one 20GP container\nDelivery time:\nAsian : 10 days, Middle East: 20 days, Africa:  30 days,\nEuropean: 30 days,\nNorth American:  20 days;\nSouth American: 30 days, Australia: 15 days; Russia: 30 days\nPayment terms:\nT/T, L/C\nSupply Ability:\n100,000 m\n2\nper month",
            "zh": "Brand Name\n:         Parete\nProduct No.:\nPRT-FS662,\nPRT-FS800,\nPRT-FS1000\nMOQ:\n10 m\n2\nUnit Price:\n25 USD/m\n2\nto 80 USD/m\n2\n(Decided by technica requirements)\nPacking:\nAbout 500 m\n2\nfor 20 GP Container\nPacking Style:\nParete Logo, Neutral,  OEM logo\nProduction time:\n7 days to 30 days, 500m2, 10 days for one 20GP container\nDelivery time:\nAsian : 10 days, Middle East: 20 days, Africa:  30 days,\nEuropean: 30 days,\nNorth American:  20 days;\nSouth American: 30 days, Australia: 15 days; Russia: 30 days\nPayment terms:\nT/T, L/C\nSupply Ability:\n100,000 m\n2\nper month"
