h=\"52\">\n<p>≥9000</p>\n</td>\n<td height=\"24\" width=\"48\">\n<p>≥910</p>\n</td>\n<td height=\"24\" width=\"59\">\n<p>≥670</p>\n</td>\n<td height=\"24\" width=\"58\">\n<p>≥31130</p>\n</td>\n<td height=\"24\" width=\"67\">\n<p>≥58000</p>\n</td>\n<td height=\"24\" width=\"60\">\n<p>6697</p>\n</td>\n<td height=\"24\" width=\"47\">\n<p>5596</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"bare finish steel raised floor panel\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/C4-OA 600-Steel raised floor with stringer-5.jpg\" height=\"552\" src=\"images/shared/images_C4-OA_600-Steel_raised_floor_with_stringer-5.jpg\" title=\"bare finish steel raised floor panel\" width=\"940\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"bare finish steel raised floor panel\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/C4-OA 600-Steel raised floor with stringer-6.jpg\" height=\"592\" src=\"images/shared/images_C4-OA_600-Steel_raised_floor_with_stringer-6.jpg\" title=\"bare finish steel raised floor panel\" width=\"940\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"bare finish steel raised floor panel\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/C4-OA 600-Steel raised floor with stringer-7.jpg\" height=\"626\" src=\"images/shared/images_C4-OA_600-Steel_raised_floor_with_stringer-7.jpg\" title=\"bare finish steel raised floor panel\" width=\"940\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"bare finish steel raised floor panel\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/C4-OA 600-Steel raised floor with stringer-0.jpg\" height=\"1216\" src=\"images/shared/images_C4-OA_600-Steel_raised_floor_with_stringer-0.jpg\" title=\"bare finish steel raised floor panel\" width=\"940\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"bare finish steel raised floor with long stringer\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/C4-OA 600-Steel raised floor with stringer-02.jpg\" height=\"528\" src=\"images/shared/images_C4-OA_600-Steel_raised_floor_with_stringer-02.jpg\" title=\"bare finish steel raised floor with long stringer\" width=\"940\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"raised floor with long stringer\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/C4-OA 600-Steel raised floor with stringer-01.jpg\" height=\"1216\" src=\"images/shared/images_C4-OA_600-Steel_raised_floor_with_stringer-01.jpg\" title=\"raised floor with long stringer\" width=\"940\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"steel raised floor with long stringer\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/C4-OA 600-Steel raised floor with stringer-01-.jpg\" height=\"726\" src=\"images/shared/images_C4-OA_600-Steel_raised_floor_with_stringer-01-.jpg\" title=\"steel raised floor with long stringer\" width=\"940\"/></p>\n<p><img alt=\"steel raised floor with long stringer in door\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/C4-OA 600-Steel raised floor with stringer-03.jpg\" height=\"1216\" src=\"images/shared/images_C4-OA_600-Steel_raised_floor_with_stringer-03.jpg\" title=\"steel raised floor with long stringer in door\" width=\"940\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> <strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Applications</span></strong></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"loading capacity\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/01-applications.jpg\" height=\"267\" src=\"images/shared/images_01-applications.jpg\" title=\"loading capacity\" width=\"900\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"steel raised floor exhibition\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/C4-OA 600-Steel raised floor with stringer-8.jpg\" height=\"703\" src=\"images/shared/images_C4-OA_600-Steel_raised_floor_with_stringer-8.jpg\" title=\"steel raised floor  exhibition\" width=\"940\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\" raised floor exhibition\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/C4-OA 600-Steel raised floor with stringer-9.jpg\" height=\"707\" src=\"images/shared/images_C4-OA_600-Steel_raised_floor_with_stringer-9.jpg\" title=\" raised floor exhibition\" width=\"940\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\" raised floor installation\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/C4-OA 600-Steel raised floor with stringer-11.JPG\" height=\"705\" src=\"images/shared/images_C4-OA_600-Steel_raised_floor_with_stringer-11.JPG\" title=\" raised floor  installation\" width=\"940\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\" raised floor  installation after cable trunk\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/C4-OA 600-Steel raised floor with stringer-12.JPG\" height=\"705\" src=\"images/shared/images_C4-OA_600-Steel_raised_floor_with_stringer-12.JPG\" title=\" raised floor  installation after cable trunk\" width=\"940\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\" raised floor  installation after cable trunk\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/C4-OA 600-Steel raised floor with stringer-13.JPG\" height=\"705\" src=\"images/shared/images_C4-OA_600-Steel_raised_floor_with_stringer-13.JPG\" title=\" raised floor  installation after cable trunk\" width=\"940\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\" raised floor  installation after cable trunk\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/C4-OA 600-Steel raised floor with stringer-14.JPG\" height=\"705\" src=\"images/shared/images_C4-OA_600-Steel_raised_floor_with_stringer-14.JPG\" title=\" raised floor  installation after cable trunk\" width=\"940\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\" raised floor  installation to curtai wall\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/C4-OA 600-Steel raised floor with stringer-16.JPG\" height=\"705\" src=\"images/shared/images_C4-OA_600-Steel_raised_floor_with_stringer-16.JPG\" title=\" raised floor  installation to curtai wall\" width=\"940\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\" raised floor  installation to curtai wall\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/C4-OA 600-Steel raised floor with stringer-17.JPG\" height=\"618\" src=\"images/shared/images_C4-OA_600-Steel_raised_floor_with_stringer-17.JPG\" title=\" raised floor  installation to curtai wall\" width=\"940\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"office raised floor  installation\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/C4-OA 600-Steel raised floor with stringer-18.JPG\" height=\"705\" src=\"images/shared/images_C4-OA_600-Steel_raised_floor_with_stringer-18.JPG\" title=\"office raised floor  installation\" width=\"940\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><img alt=\"square column go through raised floor\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/C4-OA 600-Steel raised floor with stringer-19.JPG\" height=\"705\" src=\"images/shared/images_C4-OA_600-Steel_raised_floor_with_stringer-19.JPG\" title=\"square column go through raised floor\" width=\"940\"/></span></strong></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"Round column go through raised floor\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/C4-OA 600-Steel raised floor with stringer-20.JPG\" height=\"705\" src=\"images/shared/images_C4-OA_600-Steel_raised_floor_with_stringer-20.JPG\" title=\"round column go through raised floor\" width=\"940\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\" raised floor for better cabling\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/C4-OA 600-Steel raised floor with stringer-21.JPG\" height=\"705\" src=\"images/shared/images_C4-OA_600-Steel_raised_floor_with_stringer-21.JPG\" title=\" raised floor for better cabling\" width=\"940\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\" raised floor corner cutting\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/C4-OA 600-Steel raised floor with stringer-22.JPG\" height=\"705\" src=\"images/shared/images_C4-OA_600-Steel_raised_floor_with_stringer-22.JPG\" title=\" raised floor corner cutting\" width=\"940\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\" raised floor applications\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/C4-OA 600-Steel raised floor with stringer-23.jpg\" height=\"834\" src=\"images/shared/images_C4-OA_600-Steel_raised_floor_with_stringer-23.jpg\" title=\" raised floor applications\" width=\"940\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><br/></span></strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n</ul>"
