          "description": {
            "en": {
              "text": "Steel Bare finish raised floor for office application (OA-C1)-Trunk Raised Floor\nProduct discription\nOffice steel raised\naccess floo r is specifically designed for office buildingit is convenient for cabling and wiring. Square holes could be cut or perforated for the electrical oulets. When all the work underfloor finish, the carpet will cover on the raised floor surface.\nProduct advantages:\n1. Made of steel plate, high mechanical strength, high loading capacity, good fire resistance.\n2. Epoxy power painting on surface, matt and soft, wear resistant and anti-corrosion.\n3. Covering is glued under high pressure.  Multiple choices and good decorated surface. Wear resistant and anti scratch, excellent electrical conductivity, anti pollution and easy cleaning.\n4. High dimensional accuracy,  interchangeable, flexible assembly, easy maintenance.\n5. Products can be upgraded or adjusted according to the loading requirements.\nTechnical data of steel anti-static access floor\nApplications\nThe worker is installing the steel raised floor with trunk on site (500*500*28mm)",
              "html": "<p><span style=\"font-weight: bold; font-size: x-large; line-height: 1.5;\">Steel Bare finish raised floor for office application (OA-C1)-Trunk Raised Floor</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Product discription</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"border: 0px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-senif; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 15.6000003814697px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333;\"><span style=\"border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 10.5pt; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 21px; vertical-align: baseline;\">Office steel raised</span><span style=\"border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 10.5pt; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 21px; vertical-align: baseline;\"> access floo r is specifically designed for office buildingit is convenient for cabling and wiring. Square holes could be cut or perforated for the electrical oulets. When all the work underfloor finish, the carpet will cover on the raised floor surface.</span></p>\n<p style=\"border: 0px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-senif; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 15.6000003814697px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #333333;\"> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"steel raised floor with trunk\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/C1-OA500-Raised Floor-1.jpg\" height=\"640\" src=\"images/shared/images_C1-OA500-Raised_Floor-1.jpg\" title=\"steel raised floor with trunk\" width=\"1024\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"steel raised floor with cable trunk\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/C1-OA500-Raised Floor-3.jpg\" height=\"391\" src=\"images/shared/images_C1-OA500-Raised_Floor-3.jpg\" title=\"steel raised floor with cable trunk\" width=\"656\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"steel raised floor with trunk\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/C1-OA500-Raised Floor-4.jpg\" height=\"592\" src=\"images/shared/images_C1-OA500-Raised_Floor-4.jpg\" title=\"steel raised floor with trunk\" width=\"800\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"steel raised floor with trunk\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/C1-OA500-Raised Floor-2.jpg\" height=\"767\" src=\"images/shared/images_C1-OA500-Raised_Floor-2.jpg\" title=\"steel raised floor with trunk\" width=\"940\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"spot welding for steel raised floor panel\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/01-welding.jpg\" height=\"506\" src=\"images/shared/images_01-welding.jpg\" title=\"spot welding for steel raised floor panel\" width=\"900\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Product advantages:</strong></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>1. Made of steel plate, high mechanical strength, high loading capacity, good fire resistance.</p>\n<p>2. Epoxy power painting on surface, matt and soft, wear resistant and anti-corrosion.</p>\n<p>3. Covering is glued under high pressure.  Multiple choices and good decorated surface. Wear resistant and anti scratch, excellent electrical conductivity, anti pollution and easy cleaning.</p>\n<p>4. High dimensional accuracy,  interchangeable, flexible assembly, easy maintenance.</p>\n<p>5. Products can be upgraded or adjusted according to the loading requirements.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Technical data of steel anti-static access floor<span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"> </span></strong></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"access floor loading capacity\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/01-loading_capacity.png\" height=\"492\" src=\"images/shared/images_01-loading_capacity.png\" title=\"access floor loading capacity\" width=\"900\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> <strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Applications</span></strong></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"loading capacity\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/01-applications.jpg\" height=\"267\" src=\"images/shared/images_01-applications.jpg\" title=\"loading capacity\" width=\"900\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"steel raised floor installation with cable trunk\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/C1-OA500-Raised Floor-6.jpg\" height=\"696\" src=\"images/shared/images_C1-OA500-Raised_Floor-6.jpg\" title=\"steel raised floor with trunk\" width=\"940\"/></p>\n<p>The worker is installing the steel raised floor with trunk on site (500*500*28mm)</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"steel cementitious raised floor  with trunk\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/C1-OA500-Raised Floor-7.jpg\" height=\"696\" src=\"images/shared/images_C1-OA500-Raised_Floor-7.jpg\" title=\"steel cementitious raised floor with trunk\" width=\"940\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"steel cementitious raised floor with trunk\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/C1-OA500-Raised Floor-8.jpg\" height=\"696\" src=\"images/shared/images_C1-OA500-Raised_Floor-8.jpg\" title=\"steel cementitious raised floor with trunk\" width=\"940\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"steel cementitious raised floor with trunk\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/C1-OA500-Raised Floor-10.jpg\" height=\"592\" src=\"images/shared/images_C1-OA500-Raised_Floor-10.jpg\" title=\"steel cementitious raised floor with trunk\" width=\"800\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"steel cementitious raised floor with trunk\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/C1-OA500-Raised Floor-9.jpg\" height=\"948\" src=\"images/shared/images_C1-OA500-Raised_Floor-9.jpg\" style=\"line-height: 1.5;\" title=\"steel cementitious raised floor with trunk\" width=\"1280\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"steel cementitious raised floor with trunk\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/C1-OA500-Raised Floor-11.jpg\" height=\"696\" src=\"images/shared/images_C1-OA500-Raised_Floor-11.jpg\" title=\"steel cementitious raised floor with trunk\" width=\"940\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"steel OA raised floor with trunk\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/C1-OA500-Raised Floor-12.jpg\" height=\"592\" src=\"images/shared/images_C1-OA500-Raised_Floor-12.jpg\" title=\"steel OA raised floor with trunk\" width=\"800\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"office raised floor with trunk\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/C1-OA500-Raised Floor-12.jpg\" height=\"592\" src=\"images/shared/images_C1-OA500-Raised_Floor-12.jpg\" title=\"steel cementitious raised floor with trunk\" width=\"800\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"steel cementitious raised floor with trunk\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/C1-OA500-Raised Floor-13.jpg\" height=\"592\" src=\"images/shared/images_C1-OA500-Raised_Floor-13.jpg\" title=\"steel cementitious raised floor with trunk\" width=\"800\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"steel cementitious raised floor with trunk\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/C1-OA500-Raised Floor-14.jpg\" height=\"696\" src=\"images/shared/images_C1-OA500-Raised_Floor-14.jpg\" title=\"steel cementitious raised floor with trunk\" width=\"940\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"steel cementitious raised floor with trunk\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/C1-OA500-Raised Floor-15.jpg\" height=\"592\" src=\"images/shared/images_C1-OA500-Raised_Floor-15.jpg\" title=\"steel cementitious raised floor with trunk\" width=\"800\"/></p>\n<ul>\n</ul>"
            },
            "zh": {
              "text": "Steel Bare finish raised floor for office application (OA-C1)\nProduct discription\nAntistatic Access Floor is made of good quality cold-rolled steel sheet with foaming cement fully filled. The  bottom is high quality deep stretch coil steel plate. The top is  cold rolled hard plate. The top steel plate and bottom steel plate are spot-welded to form a high quality shell. The shell is treated by phosphate and painted with epoxy powder coating. Then foaming cement will be filled into the shell. After curing, the structure will be stable and strong to support the designed loading capacity . The access floor panel has high strength and high durability.\nProduct advantages:\n1. Made of steel plate, high mechanical strength, high loading capacity, good fire resistance.\n2. Epoxy power painting on surface, matt and soft, wear resistant and anti-corrosion.\n3. Covering is glued under high pressure.  Multiple choices and good decorated surface. Wear resistant and anti scratch, excellent electrical conductivity, anti pollution and easy cleaning.\n4. High dimensional accuracy,  interchangeable, flexible assembly, easy maintenance.\n5. Products can be upgraded or adjusted according to the loading requirements.\nTechnical data of steel anti-static access floor\nApplications",
              "html": "<p><span style=\"font-weight: bold; font-size: x-large; line-height: 1.5;\">Steel Bare finish raised floor for office application (OA-C1)</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Product discription</strong></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>Antistatic Access Floor is made of good quality cold-rolled steel sheet with foaming cement fully filled. The  bottom is high quality deep stretch coil steel plate. The top is  cold rolled hard plate. The top steel plate and bottom steel plate are spot-welded to form a high quality shell. The shell is treated by phosphate and painted with epoxy powder coating. Then foaming cement will be filled into the shell. After curing, the structure will be stable and strong to support the designed loading capacity . The access floor panel has high strength and high durability.</p>\n<p><img alt=\"steel raised floor with trunk\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/C1-OA500-Raised Floor-1.jpg\" height=\"640\" src=\"images/shared/images_C1-OA500-Raised_Floor-1.jpg\" title=\"steel raised floor with trunk\" width=\"1024\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"steel raised floor with cable trunk\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/C1-OA500-Raised Floor-3.jpg\" height=\"391\" src=\"images/shared/images_C1-OA500-Raised_Floor-3.jpg\" title=\"steel raised floor with cable trunk\" width=\"656\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"steel raised floor with trunk\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/C1-OA500-Raised Floor-4.jpg\" height=\"592\" src=\"images/shared/images_C1-OA500-Raised_Floor-4.jpg\" title=\"steel raised floor with trunk\" width=\"800\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"steel raised floor with trunk\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/C1-OA500-Raised Floor-2.jpg\" height=\"767\" src=\"images/shared/images_C1-OA500-Raised_Floor-2.jpg\" title=\"steel raised floor with trunk\" width=\"940\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Product advantages:</strong></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>1. Made of steel plate, high mechanical strength, high loading capacity, good fire resistance.</p>\n<p>2. Epoxy power painting on surface, matt and soft, wear resistant and anti-corrosion.</p>\n<p>3. Covering is glued under high pressure.  Multiple choices and good decorated surface. Wear resistant and anti scratch, excellent electrical conductivity, anti pollution and easy cleaning.</p>\n<p>4. High dimensional accuracy,  interchangeable, flexible assembly, easy maintenance.</p>\n<p>5. Products can be upgraded or adjusted according to the loading requirements.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Technical data of steel anti-static access floor<span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"> </span></strong></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"access floor loading capacity\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/01-loading_capacity.png\" height=\"492\" src=\"images/shared/images_01-loading_capacity.png\" title=\"access floor loading capacity\" width=\"900\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> <strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Applications</span></strong></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"loading capacity\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/01-applications.jpg\" height=\"267\" src=\"images/shared/images_01-applications.jpg\" title=\"loading capacity\" width=\"900\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"steel raised floor installation with cable trunk\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/C1-OA500-Raised Floor-6.jpg\" height=\"696\" src=\"images/shared/images_C1-OA500-Raised_Floor-6.jpg\" title=\"steel raised floor with trunk\" width=\"940\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"steel cementitious raised floor  with trunk\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/C1-OA500-Raised Floor-7.jpg\" height=\"696\" src=\"images/shared/images_C1-OA500-Raised_Floor-7.jpg\" title=\"steel cementitious raised floor with trunk\" width=\"940\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"steel cementitious raised floor with trunk\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/C1-OA500-Raised Floor-8.jpg\" height=\"696\" src=\"images/shared/images_C1-OA500-Raised_Floor-8.jpg\" title=\"steel cementitious raised floor with trunk\" width=\"940\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"steel cementitious raised floor with trunk\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/C1-OA500-Raised Floor-10.jpg\" height=\"592\" src=\"images/shared/images_C1-OA500-Raised_Floor-10.jpg\" title=\"steel cementitious raised floor with trunk\" width=\"800\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"steel cementitious raised floor with trunk\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/C1-OA500-Raised Floor-9.jpg\" height=\"948\" src=\"images/shared/images_C1-OA500-Raised_Floor-9.jpg\" style=\"line-height: 1.5;\" title=\"steel cementitious raised floor with trunk\" width=\"1280\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"steel cementitious raised floor with trunk\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/C1-OA500-Raised Floor-11.jpg\" height=\"696\" src=\"images/shared/images_C1-OA500-Raised_Floor-11.jpg\" title=\"steel cementitious raised floor with trunk\" width=\"940\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"steel OA raised floor with trunk\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/C1-OA500-Raised Floor-12.jpg\" height=\"592\" src=\"images/shared/images_C1-OA500-Raised_Floor-12.jpg\" title=\"steel OA raised floor with trunk\" width=\"800\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"office raised floor with trunk\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/C1-OA500-Raised Floor-12.jpg\" height=\"592\" src=\"images/shared/images_C1-OA500-Raised_Floor-12.jpg\" title=\"steel cementitious raised floor with trunk\" width=\"800\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"steel cementitious raised floor with trunk\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/C1-OA500-Raised Floor-13.jpg\" height=\"592\" src=\"images/shared/images_C1-OA500-Raised_Floor-13.jpg\" title=\"steel cementitious raised floor with trunk\" width=\"800\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"steel cementitious raised floor with trunk\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/C1-OA500-Raised Floor-14.jpg\" height=\"696\" src=\"images/shared/images_C1-OA500-Raised_Floor-14.jpg\" title=\"steel cementitious raised floor with trunk\" width=\"940\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"steel cementitious raised floor with trunk\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/C1-OA500-Raised Floor-15.jpg\" height=\"592\" src=\"images/shared/images_C1-OA500-Raised_Floor-15.jpg\" title=\"steel cementitious raised floor with trunk\" width=\"800\"/></p>\n<ul>\n</ul>"
