          "description": {
            "en": {
              "text": "Aluminum Ventilation Access Floor with ESD HPL or PVC covering\nProduct discription\nAluminum access floor panel is cast from aluminum ingot in high press and vacuum environment. The surface treatment can be epoxy powder coating painting or Nickel and Chrome electroplating to achieve appearance of soft light, anti-corrosion, wear resistance and stable character. PVC or HPL  can be glue on the surface in high pressure. Aluminum access floor panel  is the most high-class in all kinds of access floor.\nProduct advantages:\nAdvantages：\n1. Innovated structure design, high dimensional accuracy, difficult to deformation;\n2. Light weight and high strength, good loading capacity;\n3. Waterproof, fireproof, anti-corrosion, anti-magnetic, non-radiation and environment friendly;\n4. Stable structure and never weakening, good conductivity;\n5. Economical and recyclable.\nAluminum Access Floor Accessories (European Style Head)\nAluminum Access Floor Accessories （Round Head System)\nTechnical data of steel anti-static access floor\nAluminum Access Floor Structure\nHPL covering\nAfter using a variety of special paper phenolic, melamine, resin processing, high temperature and pressure made of thermosetting resin decorative laminates. It is not only bright color, bright and smooth, and has a wear-resistant, heat resistance, pollution, washable and permanent decorative features, the standard thickness of 0.8mm, 1.0mm, 1.2mm, 1.5mm, the thickness can development of user requirements.\nHigh pressure melamine laminate is widely used in varies computer rooms and data centers. It is anti-static, anti-wear and free of pollution.  It is anti scratch and wear resistance. It is economical and easy glued on the surface of metal, calcium sulphate panel and wood core surface. So it is the most welcome floor covering.\nPVC covering\nConductive particles forms a special material with a perfect permanent conductivity. The conductivity makes the tile free of dust and easy to clean or maintain. Fire-proof rating FV-0 grade. Durable, waterproof, anti-chemical corrosion. It bears heavy load. Excellent tones and textures. Marbling appearance. Better flexibility. It is comfortable to walk through and hardly damage due to collision.\nIt is often used in the following areas: Electronics workshop/Manufacturing plant, Big computer room/ computer server room, Clean room, Packaging workshop, Telecommunication room, Hospital equipment room.\nApplications\nHigh standard computer room of bank, military, government or companies, or the area of cleaning room, or some area that have high requirement to loading capacity and material.\nCleaning room\nData center access floor/ raised floor",
              "html": "<p><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"line-height: 36px;\"><strong>Aluminum Ventilation Access Floor with ESD HPL or PVC covering</strong></span></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Product discription</strong></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>Aluminum access floor panel is cast from aluminum ingot in high press and vacuum environment. The surface treatment can be epoxy powder coating painting or Nickel and Chrome electroplating to achieve appearance of soft light, anti-corrosion, wear resistance and stable character. PVC or HPL  can be glue on the surface in high pressure. Aluminum access floor panel  is the most high-class in all kinds of access floor.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"aluminum access floor\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/af-12-solid_aluminum.png\" height=\"368\" src=\"images/shared/images_af-12-solid_aluminum.png\" title=\"aluminum access floor\" width=\"900\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"aluminum access floor\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/af-12-in.jpg\" height=\"402\" src=\"images/shared/images_af-12-in.jpg\" title=\"aluminum access floor\" width=\"588\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Product advantages:</strong></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>Advantages：</p>\n<p>1. Innovated structure design, high dimensional accuracy, difficult to deformation;</p>\n<p>2. Light weight and high strength, good loading capacity;</p>\n<p>3. Waterproof, fireproof, anti-corrosion, anti-magnetic, non-radiation and environment friendly;</p>\n<p>4. Stable structure and never weakening, good conductivity;</p>\n<p>5. Economical and recyclable.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Aluminum Access Floor Accessories (European Style Head)</strong></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong><img alt=\"aluminum access floor\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/af-12-alumium2.png\" height=\"611\" src=\"images/shared/images_af-12-alumium2.png\" title=\"aluminum access floor\" width=\"803\"/></strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Aluminum Access Floor Accessories （Round Head System)</strong></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"aluminum access floor\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/af-12-.png\" height=\"733\" src=\"images/shared/images_af-12-.png\" title=\"aluminum access floor\" width=\"834\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Technical data of steel anti-static access floor<span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"> </span></strong></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"aluminum access floor\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/af-12-loading-n.png\" height=\"426\" src=\"images/shared/images_af-12-loading-n.png\" title=\"aluminum access floor\" width=\"900\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium; font-weight: bold; line-height: 24px;\">Aluminum Access Floor Structure</span></p>\n<p><img alt=\"aluminum access floor\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/af12-a1.jpg\" height=\"690\" src=\"images/shared/images_af12-a1.jpg\" title=\"aluminum access floor\" width=\"900\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium; font-weight: bold; line-height: 24px;\"><img alt=\"aluminum access floor\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/af12-a2.jpg\" height=\"588\" src=\"images/shared/images_af12-a2.jpg\" title=\"aluminum access floor\" width=\"900\"/></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"aluminum access floor\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/af12-a3.jpg\" height=\"597\" src=\"images/shared/images_af12-a3.jpg\" title=\"aluminum access floor\" width=\"900\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"aluminum access floor\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/af12-a4.jpg\" height=\"606\" src=\"images/shared/images_af12-a4.jpg\" title=\"aluminum access floor\" width=\"900\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"aluminum access floor\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/af12-a5.jpg\" height=\"600\" src=\"images/shared/images_af12-a5.jpg\" title=\"aluminum access floor\" width=\"900\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"aluminum access floor\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/af12-a6.jpg\" height=\"604\" src=\"images/shared/images_af12-a6.jpg\" title=\"aluminum access floor\" width=\"900\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"aluminum access floor\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/af12-a7.jpg\" height=\"597\" src=\"images/shared/images_af12-a7.jpg\" title=\"aluminum access floor\" width=\"900\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"aluminum access floor\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/af12-a8.jpg\" height=\"598\" src=\"images/shared/images_af12-a8.jpg\" title=\"aluminum access floor\" width=\"900\"/><img alt=\"aluminum access floor\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/af12-a11.jpg\" height=\"595\" src=\"images/shared/images_af12-a11.jpg\" title=\"aluminum access floor\" width=\"900\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"aluminum access floor\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/af12-a12.jpg\" height=\"600\" src=\"images/shared/images_af12-a12.jpg\" title=\"aluminum access floor\" width=\"900\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">HPL covering</span></strong></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>After using a variety of special paper phenolic, melamine, resin processing, high temperature and pressure made of thermosetting resin decorative laminates. It is not only bright color, bright and smooth, and has a wear-resistant, heat resistance, pollution, washable and permanent decorative features, the standard thickness of 0.8mm, 1.0mm, 1.2mm, 1.5mm, the thickness can development of user requirements.</p>\n<p>High pressure melamine laminate is widely used in varies computer rooms and data centers. It is anti-static, anti-wear and free of pollution.  It is anti scratch and wear resistance. It is economical and easy glued on the surface of metal, calcium sulphate panel and wood core surface. So it is the most welcome floor covering.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"Steel access floor HPL covering\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/01-steel_hpl_covering.png\" height=\"422\" src=\"images/shared/images_01-steel_hpl_covering.png\" title=\"Steel access floor HPL covering\" width=\"900\"/></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>PVC covering</strong></span></p>\n<p>Conductive particles forms a special material with a perfect permanent conductivity. The conductivity makes the tile free of dust and easy to clean or maintain. Fire-proof rating FV-0 grade. Durable, waterproof, anti-chemical corrosion. It bears heavy load. Excellent tones and textures. Marbling appearance. Better flexibility. It is comfortable to walk through and hardly damage due to collision.</p>\n<p>It is often used in the following areas: Electronics workshop/Manufacturing plant, Big computer room/ computer server room, Clean room, Packaging workshop, Telecommunication room, Hospital equipment room.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"aluminum access floor with PVC\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/af-12-pvc.png\" height=\"321\" src=\"images/shared/images_af-12-pvc.png\" title=\"aluminum access floor with PVC\" width=\"900\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> <strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Applications</span></strong></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>High standard computer room of bank, military, government or companies, or the area of cleaning room, or some area that have high requirement to loading capacity and material.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"cleaning room access floor\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/af12-app1.jpg\" height=\"605\" src=\"images/shared/images_af12-app1.jpg\" title=\"cleaning room access floor\" width=\"750\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"cleaning room access floor\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/af12-app2.jpg\" height=\"562\" src=\"images/shared/images_af12-app2.jpg\" title=\"cleaning room access floor\" width=\"750\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"cleaning room access floor\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/af-12-app3.jpg\" height=\"562\" src=\"images/shared/images_af-12-app3.jpg\" title=\"cleaning room access floor\" width=\"750\"/></p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Cleaning room</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"aluminum access floor\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/af-12-app4.jpg\" height=\"593\" src=\"images/shared/images_af-12-app4.jpg\" title=\"data center floor\" width=\"900\"/></p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Data center access floor/ raised floor</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><br/></span></p>\n<ul>\n</ul>"
            },
