          "description": {
            "en": {
              "text": "Steel perforated access floor for Ventilation (VF-1)\nProduct discription\nThe shell is similar to the anti-static steel access floor panel. But the inside of the shell is empty without cement. The bottom and top steel plate is perforated or some type of bottom will reinforced by rids. The perforated access floor panel is used the areas that need ventilation. It will be often used together with the steel anti-static access floor. The perforated rate will be from 17% to 50% according to the requirements of the application. The covering will be HPL, PVC or ceramic tile. Steel perforated panels is also called Air Flow panel because of many holes drilled through them. Perforated panels are of accurate size and thickness, interchangeable with steel access floor panels, wood core panels or calcium sulphate panels. Specially designed and well manufactured damper is also available for perforated panels.\nThe steel ventilation access floor system                                        The right side and back side\nThe panle with balck (white) conductive PVC edge                                                                                  The panel without PVC edge\nProduct advantages:\n1. Made of steel plate, high mechanical strength, high loading capacity, good fire resistance.\n2. Interchangeable with wood core panel/calcium sulphate panel\n3. Provide superior cooling for managing heat loads in mission critical facilities\n4, The ventilation rate will be 17%～45% and can satisfy different requirements of cleaning room.\nTechnical data of steel anti-static access floor\nHPL covering\nAfter using a variety of special paper phenolic, melamine, resin processing, high temperature and pressure made of thermosetting resin decorative laminates. It is not only bright color, bright and smooth, and has a wear-resistant, heat resistance, pollution, washable and permanent decorative features, the standard thickness of 0.8mm, 1.0mm, 1.2mm, 1.5mm, the thickness can development of user requirements.\nHigh pressure melamine laminate is widely used in varies computer rooms and data centers. It is anti-static, anti-wear and free of pollution.  It is anti scratch and wear resistance. It is economical and easy glued on the surface of metal, calcium sulphate panel and wood core surface. So it is the most welcome floor covering.\nApplications",
              "html": "<p><span style=\"font-weight: bold; font-size: x-large; line-height: 1.5;\">Steel perforated access floor for Ventilation (VF-1)</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Product discription</strong></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>The shell is similar to the anti-static steel access floor panel. But the inside of the shell is empty without cement. The bottom and top steel plate is perforated or some type of bottom will reinforced by rids. The perforated access floor panel is used the areas that need ventilation. It will be often used together with the steel anti-static access floor. The perforated rate will be from 17% to 50% according to the requirements of the application. The covering will be HPL, PVC or ceramic tile. Steel perforated panels is also called Air Flow panel because of many holes drilled through them. Perforated panels are of accurate size and thickness, interchangeable with steel access floor panels, wood core panels or calcium sulphate panels. Specially designed and well manufactured damper is also available for perforated panels.</p>\n<p><img alt=\"ventilation access  floor\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/steel_ventilation_floor-vf1-21-0.jpg\" height=\"467\" src=\"images/40-steel-ventilation-access-floor/images_steel_ventilation_floor-vf1-21-0.jpg\" title=\"ventilation raised floor\" width=\"901\"/></p>\n<p>                                     The steel ventilation access floor system                                        The right side and back side </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"ventilation access  floor\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/steel_ventilation_floor-vf1-21.png\" height=\"419\" src=\"images/40-steel-ventilation-access-floor/images_steel_ventilation_floor-vf1-21.png\" title=\"ventilation access  floor\" width=\"900\"/></p>\n<p>            The panle with balck (white) conductive PVC edge                                                                                  The panel without PVC edge</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"ventilation \" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/steel_ventilation_floor-vf1-21-01.jpg\" src=\"images/40-steel-ventilation-access-floor/images_steel_ventilation_floor-vf1-21-01.jpg\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\" title=\"ventilation raised floor\"/></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Product advantages:</strong></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>1. Made of steel plate, high mechanical strength, high loading capacity, good fire resistance.</p>\n<p>2. Interchangeable with wood core panel/calcium sulphate panel</p>\n<p>3. Provide superior cooling for managing heat loads in mission critical facilities</p>\n<p>4, The ventilation rate will be 17%～45% and can satisfy different requirements of cleaning room.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Technical data of steel anti-static access floor<span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"> </span></strong></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><br/></span></strong></span></p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">HPL covering</span></strong></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>After using a variety of special paper phenolic, melamine, resin processing, high temperature and pressure made of thermosetting resin decorative laminates. It is not only bright color, bright and smooth, and has a wear-resistant, heat resistance, pollution, washable and permanent decorative features, the standard thickness of 0.8mm, 1.0mm, 1.2mm, 1.5mm, the thickness can development of user requirements.</p>\n<p>High pressure melamine laminate is widely used in varies computer rooms and data centers. It is anti-static, anti-wear and free of pollution.  It is anti scratch and wear resistance. It is economical and easy glued on the surface of metal, calcium sulphate panel and wood core surface. So it is the most welcome floor covering.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"Steel access floor HPL covering\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/01-steel_hpl_covering.png\" height=\"422\" src=\"images/shared/images_01-steel_hpl_covering.png\" title=\"Steel access floor HPL covering\" width=\"900\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> <strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Applications</span></strong></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"loading capacity\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/01-applications.jpg\" height=\"267\" src=\"images/shared/images_01-applications.jpg\" title=\"loading capacity\" width=\"900\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"ventilation raised floor\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/steel_ventilation_floor-vf1-21-01.jpg\" height=\"675\" src=\"images/40-steel-ventilation-access-floor/images_steel_ventilation_floor-vf1-21-01.jpg\" title=\"ventilation raised floor\" width=\"900\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><img alt=\"ventilation raised floor\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/steel_ventilation_floor-vf1-21-1.jpg\" height=\"675\" src=\"images/40-steel-ventilation-access-floor/images_steel_ventilation_floor-vf1-21-1.jpg\" title=\"ventilation raised floor\" width=\"900\"/></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"ventilation raised floor\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/steel_ventilation_floor-vf1-21-2.jpg\" height=\"675\" src=\"images/40-steel-ventilation-access-floor/images_steel_ventilation_floor-vf1-21-2.jpg\" title=\"ventilation raised floor\" width=\"900\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"ventilation raised floor\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/steel_ventilation_floor-vf1-21-3.jpg\" height=\"675\" src=\"images/40-steel-ventilation-access-floor/images_steel_ventilation_floor-vf1-21-3.jpg\" title=\"ventilation raised floor\" width=\"900\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"ventilation access floor with esd pvc\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/steel_ventilation_floor-vf1-21-10.jpg\" height=\"675\" src=\"images/40-steel-ventilation-access-floor/images_steel_ventilation_floor-vf1-21-10.jpg\" title=\"ventilation access floor with esd pvc\" width=\"900\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><img alt=\"ventilation raised floor\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/steel_ventilation_floor-vf1-21-4.jpg\" height=\"675\" src=\"images/40-steel-ventilation-access-floor/images_steel_ventilation_floor-vf1-21-4.jpg\" title=\"ventilation raised floor\" width=\"900\"/></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"ventilation raised floor\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/steel_ventilation_floor-vf1-21-5.jpg\" height=\"675\" src=\"images/40-steel-ventilation-access-floor/images_steel_ventilation_floor-vf1-21-5.jpg\" title=\"ventilation raised floor\" width=\"900\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"ventilation raised floor\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/steel_ventilation_floor-vf1-21-6.jpg\" height=\"675\" src=\"images/40-steel-ventilation-access-floor/images_steel_ventilation_floor-vf1-21-6.jpg\" title=\"ventilation access floor with esd pvc\" width=\"900\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"ventilation access floor with esd pvc\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/steel_ventilation_floor-vf1-21-7.jpg\" height=\"675\" src=\"images/40-steel-ventilation-access-floor/images_steel_ventilation_floor-vf1-21-7.jpg\" title=\"ventilation access floor with esd pvc\" width=\"900\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"ventilation access floor with esd pvc\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/steel_ventilation_floor-vf1-21-8.jpg\" height=\"675\" src=\"images/40-steel-ventilation-access-floor/images_steel_ventilation_floor-vf1-21-8.jpg\" title=\"ventilation access floor with esd pvc\" width=\"900\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"ventilation access floor with esd pvc\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/steel_ventilation_floor-vf1-21-9.jpg\" height=\"675\" src=\"images/40-steel-ventilation-access-floor/images_steel_ventilation_floor-vf1-21-9.jpg\" title=\"ventilation access floor with esd pvc\" width=\"900\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"ventilation access floor with esd pvc\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/steel_ventilation_floor-vf1-21-11.jpg\" height=\"675\" src=\"images/40-steel-ventilation-access-floor/images_steel_ventilation_floor-vf1-21-11.jpg\" title=\"ventilation access floor with esd pvc\" width=\"900\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"ventilation access floor with esd pvc\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/steel_ventilation_floor-vf1-21-12.jpg\" height=\"675\" src=\"images/40-steel-ventilation-access-floor/images_steel_ventilation_floor-vf1-21-12.jpg\" title=\"ventilation access floor with esd pvc\" width=\"900\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><img alt=\"ventilation access floor with esd pvc\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/steel_ventilation_floor-vf1-21-13.jpg\" height=\"790\" src=\"images/40-steel-ventilation-access-floor/images_steel_ventilation_floor-vf1-21-13.jpg\" title=\"ventilation access floor with esd pvc\" width=\"900\"/></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"ventilation access floor with esd pvc\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/steel_ventilation_floor-vf1-21-14.jpg\" height=\"675\" src=\"images/40-steel-ventilation-access-floor/images_steel_ventilation_floor-vf1-21-14.jpg\" title=\"ventilation access floor with esd pvc\" width=\"900\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<ul>\n</ul>"
            },
            "zh": {
              "text": "Steel perforated access floor for Ventilation\nProduct discription\nThe shell is similar to the anti-static steel access floor panel. But the inside of the shell is empty without cement. The bottom and top steel plate is perforated or some type of bottom will reinforced by rids. The perforated access floor panel is used the areas that need ventilation. It will be often used together with the steel anti-static access floor. The perforated rate will be from 17% to 50% according to the requirements of the application. The covering will be HPL, PVC or ceramic tile. Steel perforated panels is also called Air Flow panel because of many holes drilled through them. Perforated panels are of accurate size and thickness, interchangeable with steel access floor panels, wood core panels or calcium sulphate panels. Specially designed and well manufactured damper is also available for perforated panels.\nProduct advantages:\n1. Made of steel plate, high mechanical strength, high loading capacity, good fire resistance.\n2. Interchangeable with wood core panel/calcium sulphate panel\n3. Provide superior cooling for managing heat loads in mission critical facilities\n4, The ventilation rate will be 17%～45% and can satisfy different requirements of cleaning room.\nTechnical data of steel anti-static access floor\nHPL covering\nAfter using a variety of special paper phenolic, melamine, resin processing, high temperature and pressure made of thermosetting resin decorative laminates. It is not only bright color, bright and smooth, and has a wear-resistant, heat resistance, pollution, washable and permanent decorative features, the standard thickness of 0.8mm, 1.0mm, 1.2mm, 1.5mm, the thickness can development of user requirements.\nHigh pressure melamine laminate is widely used in varies computer rooms and data centers. It is anti-static, anti-wear and free of pollution.  It is anti scratch and wear resistance. It is economical and easy glued on the surface of metal, calcium sulphate panel and wood core surface. So it is the most welcome floor covering.\nApplications\nAnti static access floor used in Computer room\nUPS room raised access floor / raised floor\ncontrol room raised floor\nComputer room raised floor\nControl Center access floor/ mornintoring room access floor\nCollege teaching room access floor / computer room raised floor",
              "html": "<p><span style=\"font-weight: bold; font-size: x-large; line-height: 1.5;\">Steel perforated access floor for Ventilation</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Product discription</strong></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>The shell is similar to the anti-static steel access floor panel. But the inside of the shell is empty without cement. The bottom and top steel plate is perforated or some type of bottom will reinforced by rids. The perforated access floor panel is used the areas that need ventilation. It will be often used together with the steel anti-static access floor. The perforated rate will be from 17% to 50% according to the requirements of the application. The covering will be HPL, PVC or ceramic tile. Steel perforated panels is also called Air Flow panel because of many holes drilled through them. Perforated panels are of accurate size and thickness, interchangeable with steel access floor panels, wood core panels or calcium sulphate panels. Specially designed and well manufactured damper is also available for perforated panels.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Product advantages:</strong></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>1. Made of steel plate, high mechanical strength, high loading capacity, good fire resistance.</p>\n<p>2. Interchangeable with wood core panel/calcium sulphate panel</p>\n<p>3. Provide superior cooling for managing heat loads in mission critical facilities</p>\n<p>4, The ventilation rate will be 17%～45% and can satisfy different requirements of cleaning room.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Technical data of steel anti-static access floor<span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"> </span></strong></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"access floor loading capacity\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/01-loading_capacity.png\" height=\"492\" src=\"images/shared/images_01-loading_capacity.png\" title=\"access floor loading capacity\" width=\"900\"/></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><br/></span></strong></span></p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">HPL covering</span></strong></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>After using a variety of special paper phenolic, melamine, resin processing, high temperature and pressure made of thermosetting resin decorative laminates. It is not only bright color, bright and smooth, and has a wear-resistant, heat resistance, pollution, washable and permanent decorative features, the standard thickness of 0.8mm, 1.0mm, 1.2mm, 1.5mm, the thickness can development of user requirements.</p>\n<p>High pressure melamine laminate is widely used in varies computer rooms and data centers. It is anti-static, anti-wear and free of pollution.  It is anti scratch and wear resistance. It is economical and easy glued on the surface of metal, calcium sulphate panel and wood core surface. So it is the most welcome floor covering.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"Steel access floor HPL covering\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/01-steel_hpl_covering.png\" height=\"422\" src=\"images/shared/images_01-steel_hpl_covering.png\" title=\"Steel access floor HPL covering\" width=\"900\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> <strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Applications</span></strong></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"loading capacity\" data-original-src=\"https://www.parete.net/upload/images/01-applications.jpg\" height=\"267\" src=\"images/shared/images_01-applications.jpg\" title=\"loading capacity\" width=\"900\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Anti static access floor used in Computer room </span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">UPS room raised access floor / raised floor</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">control room raised floor</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Computer room raised floor</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Control Center access floor/ mornintoring room access floor</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">College teaching room access floor / computer room raised floor</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><br/></span></strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n</ul>"
            }
          },
